message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with audio and signal processing. cs.SD is followed by cs.SI, cs.LG, cs.NE, and cs.SY. cs.SI and cs.LG deal with machine learning and neural networks, which are used in the paper. cs.NE deals with neural networks and their applications, and cs.SY deals with systems and control, which can be related to the system of music transcription.
